Thus, the investigation into this nuclear case has been going on since June 2008 without a result and is "transforming increasingly into a serious problem for the credibility of the Agency", as recognized by a high-ranking Western diplomat serving at the IAEA headquarters in Vienna, in the end it is a violation of international law.
